trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderMapping" /> class represents a SOAP header mapping.
trans-unit.target: A classe <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderMapping" /> representa um mapeamento de cabeçalho SOAP.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> value that indicates whether the SOAP header mapping is custom-defined.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> que indica se o mapeamento de cabeçalho SOAP é definido de modo personalizado.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the SOAP header mapping is custom-defined; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> Se o mapeamento de cabeçalho SOAP é personalizadas; Caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderDirection" /> value that indicates the direction of the SOAP header mapping.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderDirection" /> que indica a direção do mapeamento de cabeçalho SOAP.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderDirection" /> value that indicates the direction of the SOAP header mapping.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderDirection" /> valor que indica a direção do mapeamento de cabeçalho SOAP.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.Type" /> that represents the type of the SOAP header mapping.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um <see cref="T:System.Type" /> que representa o tipo do mapeamento de cabeçalho SOAP.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Type" /> that represents the type of the SOAP header mapping.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Type" /> que representa o tipo de mapeamento de cabeçalho de SOAP.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Reflection.MemberInfo" /> associated with the SOAP header mapping.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o <see cref="T:System.Reflection.MemberInfo" /> associado com o mapeamento de cabeçalho SOAP.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Reflection.MemberInfo" /> associated with the SOAP header mapping.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Reflection.MemberInfo" /> associado com o mapeamento de cabeçalho SOAP.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> value that indicates whether the SOAP header mapping repeats.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> que indica se o mapeamento de cabeçalho SOAP se repete.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the SOAP header mapping repeats; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> Se o mapeamento de cabeçalho SOAP repete; Caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.
